text: Juha Petri Sipilä (; born 25 April 1961) is a Finnish politician. He was Prime Minister of Finland from 2015 to 2019. He was the leader of the Centre Party from 2012 to 2019. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Finland Category:Speakers of the Parliament of Finland
title: Juha Sipilä
